{"about_the_game":"Crimsonwood is a roguelight top-down shooter in a cursed national park. Collect weapons, gain perks and battle hordes of enemies to remove the curse. Every run reshapes the park, offering new challenges.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/battle1.gif?t=1734430854\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ARSENAL OF DESTRUCTION</h2>Discover and wield a vast array of weapons, from classic firearms to bizarre, bonemade armaments. Each weapon brings a unique strategy to the battlefield.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/battle2.gif?t=1734430854\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PERKS</h2>Unlock and combine powerful perks to create your own playstyle. Will you focus on speed, firepower, or survivability?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/battle3.gif?t=1734430854\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CURSED NATIONAL PARK</h2>Explore a once-peaceful park turned into a nightmarish battleground. Navigate through procedurally generated levels filled with corrupted landmarks and hidden dangers.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/battle4.gif?t=1734430854\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HORDES OF ENEMIES</h2>Face off against waves of corrupted creatures, each with their own attack patterns and weaknesses. From possessed park rangers to mutated wildlife, danger lurks around every corner.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/extras/battle5.gif?t=1734430854\" /><br><br>Get ready to lock, load, and face hordes of enemies.<br>Crimsonwood awaits!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734430854","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it